<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 03:12:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>官方媒体称，中国海警将菲律宾船只驱逐出黄岩岛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-coast-guard-expels-philippine-vessels-scarborough-shoal-state-media-says-2024-04-30/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，中国海警周一表示，已从黄岩岛附近海域“驱逐”了一艘菲律宾海警船和另一艘船只。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:35:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-coast-guard-expels-philippine-vessels-scarborough-shoal-state-media-says-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织称亚太经济体正走向“软着陆”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia-pacific-economies-headed-soft-landing-says-imf-2024-04-30/</link><description>国际货币基金组织（IMF）周二表示，尽管未来两年经济扩张预计将放缓，但快速通货紧缩和弹性增长将有助于亚太地区实现“软着陆”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:23:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia-pacific-economies-headed-soft-landing-says-imf-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>万科首只上市商业REIT上市后早盘下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-vankes-first-public-commercial-reit-falls-early-trade-debut-2024-04-30/</link><description>万科首个公开商业地产投资产品周二上市后早盘下跌高达3%，反映出在房地产市场长期低迷的情况下对中国第二大开发商的谨慎态度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:09:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-vankes-first-public-commercial-reit-falls-early-trade-debut-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市上涨，日元在本周开局波动后波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-30/</link><description>由于投资者等待一系列经济数据、企业盈利和美联储政策会议，亚洲股市周二小幅走高，而日元在疑似干预措施将其从 34 年低点拯救出来后一天小幅走软。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:04:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国工厂活动创14个月来最快增速</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-factory-activity-expands-fastest-clip-14-months-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-04-30/</link><description>周二的一项私人调查显示，在新出口订单强劲增长的推动下，4月份中国制造业活动以14个月以来最快的速度扩张，这对于仍在努力实现强劲复苏的经济来说是一个令人鼓舞的迹象。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:03:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-factory-activity-expands-fastest-clip-14-months-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>4月份中国工厂、服务业活动增速放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-grows-slower-pace-april-2024-04-30/</link><description>周二的官方调查显示，中国四月份制造业和服务业活动扩张速度均放缓，这表明世界第二大经济体在第二季度初的动力有所减弱。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 01:59:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-grows-slower-pace-april-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>4月份中国非制造业活动扩张放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-non-manufacturing-activity-expands-slower-pace-april-2024-04-30/</link><description>周二的一项官方调查显示，中国四月份非制造业活动扩张速度放缓，可能是由于南方地区恶劣天气对建筑和服务业造成干扰。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 01:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-non-manufacturing-activity-expands-slower-pace-april-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国四月份工厂活动增速放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-april-factory-activity-grows-slower-pace-2024-04-30/</link><description>周二的官方工厂调查显示，中国四月份制造业活动扩张速度放缓，这表明庞大的行业在第二季度初开始失去一些动力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 01:38:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-april-factory-activity-grows-slower-pace-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国反腐机构对司法部前副部长立案调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-anti-graft-watchdog-probes-former-vice-justice-minister-2024-04-30/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国司法部原副部长正接受中央纪委、国家监委纪律审查和监察调查。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 01:19:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-anti-graft-watchdog-probes-former-vice-justice-minister-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>陷入困境的中国城市难以支付购房补贴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/strained-chinese-cities-struggle-pay-home-buying-subsidies-2024-04-29/</link><description>艾米·王(Amy Wang)指望中国东部城市潍坊当局承诺提供10万元人民币（13,800美元）的补贴来装修她两年前购买的一套公寓。她还在等钱，还没有搬进去。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 23:04:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/strained-chinese-cities-struggle-pay-home-buying-subsidies-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美元兑160日元反弹，特斯拉的中国喜悦</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-29/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:46:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>秘鲁寻求避免对中国建造的大型港口进行仲裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/peru-seeks-avoid-arbitration-over-chinese-built-mega-port-2024-04-29/</link><description>一位官员周一表示，秘鲁政府正在寻求避免中国港口运营商中远海运可能就该公司正在建造的大型设施的排他权的法律纠纷提起的国际仲裁程序。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 19:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/peru-seeks-avoid-arbitration-over-chinese-built-mega-port-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>塑料谈判因产量限制陷入僵局而升温</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/plastic-treaty-talks-behind-schedule-amid-impasse-over-production-limits-2024-04-29/</link><description>由于世界对其第一个塑料条约应有多大的雄心仍存在分歧，各国正在考虑在 12 月达成预期协议之前召开一系列小型会议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 16:34:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/plastic-treaty-talks-behind-schedule-amid-impasse-over-production-limits-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>英国称到2025年将从敏感地点移除中国制造的监控套件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/chinese-made-surveillance-kit-be-removed-sensitive-sites-by-2025-says-uk-2024-04-29/</link><description>英国政府周一表示，由于对北京间谍活动的担忧日益加剧，英国希望在 2025 年 4 月之前从敏感地点移除中国制造的监控技术。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 14:49:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/chinese-made-surveillance-kit-be-removed-sensitive-sites-by-2025-says-uk-2024-04-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪第一季度盈利疲弱，价格战显现影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-shows-effects-price-war-with-weaker-profit-growth-2024-04-29/</link><description>中国电动汽车 (EV) 制造商比亚迪周一公布了自 2022 年以来最弱的季度利润增长，同时，由于电动汽车需求放缓和全球最大汽车市场激烈的价格战，其收入增长放缓至近四年来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 11:12:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-shows-effects-price-war-with-weaker-profit-growth-2024-04-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>